  <brief_title>Returning to Work. Efficacy of &quot;Tailored Physical Activity or&quot; &quot;Chronic Pain Self-management Program&quot; in Sicklisted Citizens With Chronic Musculoskeletal Pain</brief_title>
  <official_title>Efficacy of &quot;Tailored Physical Activity or&quot; &quot;Chronic Pain Self-management Program&quot; on Returning to Work: a Randomized Controlled Trial in Sicklisted Citizens With Chronic Pain Related to the Spine or Upper Body</official_title>
